{"tid":247123,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"日本皇室真子公主下嫁TOEIC 950分帥氣大學同學","createTime":"2017-05-17T14:15:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-18T12:01:55.000Z","uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0297c9d4a1349e29dbc92cdce41474c2c4ae3e7d","tid":247123,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2527/d2527227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2527%2Fd2527227.jpg&h=2e6fba75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲現年25歲的真子公主宣布婚訊，要嫁給大學同學小室圭。<br />\n<br />\n日本皇室16日傳出喜訊！秋篠宮的25歲長女真子要結婚了，對象是大學同學小室圭，兩人交往5年感情終於修成正果。而她的婚訊曝光後老公立刻被全民熱搜，原來男方大學時代擔任神奈川縣藤澤市觀光大使，當過一整年「海王子」，網友見照直呼「超帥的！」<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2527/d2527224.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2527%2Fd2527224.jpg&h=a0e0bd96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲朝日新聞以號外派發真子公主結婚喜訊。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DmtmLWn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDmtmLWn.jpg&h=69369a4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n據日本NHK電視台報導，小室圭和真子公主就讀國際基督教大學，5年前因為留學討論會在涉谷的餐廳認識，進而發展成男女朋友，兩人大多在橫濱、東京約會。他2010年擔任「湘南江之島海王子」觀光大使，大學畢業後，現在任職法律事務所，同時就讀一橋大學的研究所，網路還盛傳他多益（TOEIC）分數950分（滿分990分），五官帥氣又有點可愛，網友又驚又喜「海王子我笑了」、「王子跟公主真的結婚了」，同時觀光協會「海王子」網站瞬間塞爆了！<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2527/d2527226.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2527%2Fd2527226.jpg&h=e2c5baeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小室圭現居橫濱市北區，和真子公主交往5年，網路盛傳多益成績高達950分。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.ettoday.net/images/2527/d2527225.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2527%2Fd2527225.jpg&h=6c4abd08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲小室圭（左一）2010年曾擔任「湘南江之島海王子」，以觀光大使身分協助宣傳活動。<br />\n<br />\n依日本皇室傳統，女性皇族結婚後將會退出皇籍，成為一般平民。真子公主是明仁天皇4個孫兒中首位大婚的孩子，她婚後皇室的女性成員減為13人。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZntKEM9g3tA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZntKEM9g3tA&d=oZ19EkYl1LXsHPE32KnJvaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=3044aaf0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZntKEM9g3tA</a>"},{"pid":"d66dc505210e77a5aa620c3216c2eca94014cfac","tid":247123,"uid":49068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"人地selling point明明係海之王子同個樣<br />\n黎到香港變左toeic"},{"pid":"d965cfa79bc7d34940d12d03ee3adaf06602ed2e","tid":247123,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:27:10.000Z","msg":"佳子公主男友呢？"},{"pid":"61736c2daeb0542377294cc8009c512275b49933","tid":247123,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:34:01.000Z","msg":"帥氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"7f6a469808c10cf7fe8e59a214f5c2b95d621c83","tid":247123,"uid":2784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"馮德倫？"},{"pid":"84ab8e69d573f99a5d19b2e067fd949a267745d7","tid":247123,"uid":1349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"原來日本咁既樣已經係靚仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68d48197d0162ac14473865bde794956cd044b6","tid":247123,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T12:01:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}